|                                                              |                                                            | @Controller in OfficeFloor
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+


* Phase 3: Native OfficeFloor

  Optional.  If there is interest in removing Spring as a runtime dependency, OfficeFloor can run
  without it.  All REST YAML files, service classes, and team configurations carry over unchanged.
  The following tutorials explore the complete set of native OfficeFloor capabilities organised by
  concern.


** Core REST and Dependency Injection

  The foundation tutorials for native OfficeFloor REST applications.

*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
|| Tutorial                                                    || Description                                               || Covered
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
