*-------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| 2     | {{{./legacy/JaxRsHttpServer/index.html}JAX-RS Procedures}} | Integrate JAX-RS resource methods as OfficeFloor Procedures. | JAX-RS Procedure
*-------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| 3     | {{{./legacy/JaxRsHttpServer/migrate.html}Migrate JAX-RS}} | Remove the JAX-RS dependency and run natively on OfficeFloor. | Migrate JAX-RS
*-------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+


